# Style Guide for Krishna Shinde's Portfolio

## Fonts
- Primary Font: Poppins
- Secondary Font: Mulish

## Colors
- Background Color: #ffffff (White)
- Header Background Color: #007bff (Brighter Blue)
- Text Color: #333 (Dark Gray)
- Link Hover Color: #ffc107 (Yellow)

## Layout
- Use flexbox for navigation and layout structures.
- Ensure responsiveness for different screen sizes.
- Maintain consistent padding and margins throughout the design.

## Components
- Chatbot: Positioned fixed at the bottom left with a light background and rounded corners.
- Navigation: Fixed at the top with a smooth transition for background color on scroll.

## Additional Notes
- Ensure all images are optimized for web use.
- Validate HTML and CSS for errors before deployment.
